       <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-pink-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
        <span class="text-3xl">🥅</span>
       </div>
       <h3 class="font-bebas text-2xl text-white mb-3">Open Practice Nets</h3>
       <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">Dedicated open nets for cricket practice, allowing players to train and improve their game.</p>
       <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-green-400 font-semibold">
        <span>Book Now</span>
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewbox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
        </svg>
