   <section class="py-24 bg-slate-800/50 relative">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
     <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <span class="inline-block bg-green-500/20 text-green-400 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold mb-4">Common Questions</span>
      <h2 class="font-bebas text-5xl sm:text-6xl text-white mb-4">FAQs</h2>
     </div>
     <div class="space-y-4">
      <details class="glass-card rounded-xl p-6 border border-green-500/20 cursor-pointer group"><summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-semibold text-white text-lg hover:text-green-400 transition-colors"> <span>What are your operating hours?</span> <span class="text-2xl group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">+</span> </summary>
       <p class="text-gray-400 mt-4">We're open from 6:00 AM to 11:00 PM on weekdays and 7:00 AM to 10:00 PM on weekends. Special bookings outside these hours can be arranged by contacting us directly.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="glass-card rounded-xl p-6 border border-green-500/20 cursor-pointer group"><summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-semibold text-white text-lg hover:text-green-400 transition-colors"> <span>How do I book a slot?</span> <span class="text-2xl group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">+</span> </summary>
       <p class="text-gray-400 mt-4">Simply click on any "Book Now" button and send us a WhatsApp message with your preferred date, time, and activity. Our team will confirm your booking within 30 minutes.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="glass-card rounded-xl p-6 border border-green-500/20 cursor-pointer group"><summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-semibold text-white text-lg hover:text-green-400 transition-colors"> <span>What's the cancellation policy?</span> <span class="text-2xl group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">+</span> </summary>
       <p class="text-gray-400 mt-4">Cancellations made 24 hours before the booking receive a full refund. Cancellations within 24 hours are charged 50% of the booking amount. No-shows will be charged in full.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="glass-card rounded-xl p-6 border border-green-500/20 cursor-pointer group"><summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-semibold text-white text-lg hover:text-green-400 transition-colors"> <span>Do you provide equipment?</span> <span class="text-2xl group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">+</span> </summary>
       <p class="text-gray-400 mt-4">Basic equipment like cricket stumps and football goals are provided. Players can bring their own bats, balls, and protective gear. All equipment must be approved by our staff.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="glass-card rounded-xl p-6 border border-green-500/20 cursor-pointer group"><summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-semibold text-white text-lg hover:text-green-400 transition-colors"> <span>Are there any group discounts?</span> <span class="text-2xl group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">+</span> </summary>
       <p class="text-gray-400 mt-4">Yes! Groups of 10 or more persons get a 20% discount. We also offer special rates for regular weekly/monthly bookings and corporate team-building events.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="glass-card rounded-xl p-6 border border-green-500/20 cursor-pointer group"><summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-semibold text-white text-lg hover:text-green-400 transition-colors"> <span>Is there parking available?</span> <span class="text-2xl group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">+</span> </summary>
       <p class="text-gray-400 mt-4">Yes, ample parking space is available for our guests. Parking is free for all players. We also provide secure storage facilities for valuables during play.</p>
      </details>
     </div>
    </div>
   </section><!-- Location Section -->
